            "border_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {
            "accordion_row_andromeda_1": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Quelle est la différence entre soie 22 mommes et 19 mommes ?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_andromeda_1": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Les mommes désignent le poids du tissu. À 22 mommes, notre soie est plus dense, plus opaque et plus durable. Elle bloque 100% de la lumière et conserve sa douceur lavage après lavage.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_andromeda_1"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_andromeda_2": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Qu'est-ce que le grade 6A de la soie ?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_andromeda_2": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Le grade 6A est la classification la plus haute de la soie de mûrier. Moins de 5% de la production mondiale l'atteint. Les filaments extra-longs donnent une surface parfaitement lisse et douce.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_andromeda_2"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_andromeda_3": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Comment laver mon masque Andromeda ?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_andromeda_3": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Lavage à la main à l'eau froide avec un savon doux, ou en machine cycle délicat 30°C (filet de lavage recommandé). Séchage à plat, loin de toute chaleur.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_andromeda_3"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_andromeda_4": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "C'est quoi le QR code inclus dans ma commande ?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_andromeda_4": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Chaque masque est livré avec un QR code donnant accès à notre espace rituel exclusif — une sélection de sons d'ambiance conçus pour accompagner l'endormissement.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_andromeda_4"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_andromeda_5": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Le masque est-il adapté aux dormeurs sur le côté ?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_andromeda_5": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Oui. L'élastique réglable ne laisse aucune pression sur la tête ni marque sur la peau. Le masque reste en place toute la nuit quelle que soit votre position.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
